      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829577
    m_Localized: "This monument stands in \u0141azienki Park in Warsaw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829578
    m_Localized: "This monument stands in \u0141azienki Park in Warsaw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829579
    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are characters from an old legend about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829580
    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are characters from an old legend about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829581
    m_Localized: "King Sigismund III Vasa moved the capital of Poland from Krak\xF3w
      to Warsaw in 1596."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829582
    m_Localized: "King Sigismund III Vasa moved the capital of Poland from Krak\xF3w
      to Warsaw in 1596."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829583
    m_Localized: The Polish parliament is called the Sejm and the Senate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829584
    m_Localized: The Polish parliament is called the Sejm and the Senate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829585
    m_Localized: The Palace of Culture and Science is the tallest building in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829586
    m_Localized: The Palace of Culture and Science is the tallest building in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829587
    m_Localized: "The PGE Narodowy stands on the right bank of the Wis\u0142a."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83574578343829588
    m_Localized: "The PGE Narodowy stands on the right bank of the Wis\u0142a."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327552
    m_Localized: Great work. You explored Warsaw and reassembled the Mermaid's sword!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327553
    m_Localized: Draw your favorite place in Warsaw!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327554
    m_Localized: Hallo. Do you know where we are?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327555
    m_Localized: In Torun
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327556
    m_Localized: In Warsaw
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327557
    m_Localized: Good. It's always important to listen and read all dialogs in the
      game.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327558
    m_Localized: Maybe you could help us solving a mystery. Go to the Mermaid!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327559
    m_Localized: Hallo. Do you know where we are?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327560
    m_Localized: In Torun
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327561
    m_Localized: People travel by tram, bus, train, car, and bike.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327562
    m_Localized: "When you are done, I will give you the key to this chest. Then
      go to the Wars and Sawa statue by the Wis\u0142a river."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327563
    m_Localized: Let us sort the ways people move around Warsaw!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327564
    m_Localized: I need help. What should I sort?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327565
    m_Localized: Some people ride a bike around the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327566
    m_Localized: Many people ride the tram in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327567
    m_Localized: The Mermaid chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327568
    m_Localized: Take the card and go south to the Chopin Monument in the park. Keep
      looking for my sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327569
    m_Localized: Antura scattered the notes of my melody around the monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327570
    m_Localized: Come back and play the melody on the piano to restore it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327571
    m_Localized: Then tap them in the same order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327572
    m_Localized: I am ready to play!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327573
    m_Localized: I saw Antura run past Copernicus and toward the river with the Mermaid's
      sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327574
    m_Localized: Good try! Come back and play the melody again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327575
    m_Localized: The Chopin chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327576
    m_Localized: Go north-east and help Wars and Sawa by the Wisla.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327577
    m_Localized: Chopin needs help first. Then come to the river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327578
    m_Localized: Sawa is waiting by the river bend. Speak with her, then come back
      to Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327579
    m_Localized: I am Wars. Antura caused chaos here too, and Sawa got separated
      from me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327580
    m_Localized: "Please find her at the bend of the Wis\u0142a and bring her back
      to me."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327581
    m_Localized: Please walk back to Wars. We will tell you the rest of our story
      together.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327582
    m_Localized: Return to Wars. We are both ready.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327583
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327584
    m_Localized: Our story is one of the old stories of Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327585
    m_Localized: The Wisla flows through Warsaw, and our story is part of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327586
    m_Localized: Antura passed toward King Sigismund's Column in the old town.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327587
    m_Localized: Our chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327588
    m_Localized: Go west to the old town square and speak with King Sigismund. He
      may know where the sword was left.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327589
    m_Localized: Help Wars and Sawa first, then come to my square.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327590
    m_Localized: I moved the capital to Warsaw long ago. Today, Parliament leads
      Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327591
    m_Localized: Antura knocked three pieces of my crown off. Find them and bring
      them back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327592
    m_Localized: Excellent. My crown is complete again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327593
    m_Localized: Now I can tell you where the sword went next.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327594
    m_Localized: People remember me because the capital moved to Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327595
    m_Localized: I heard the Mermaid's sword was left at the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327596
    m_Localized: My chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327597
    m_Localized: Continue east to the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327598
    m_Localized: Please visit King Sigismund first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327599
    m_Localized: I also work near the Presidential Palace, and yes, I have the Mermaid's
      sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327600
    m_Localized: But first, the flag pieces were scattered. Sort the white and red
      parts back in the right order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327601
    m_Localized: Put them in that order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327602
    m_Localized: Let us sort the flag now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327603
    m_Localized: Here is the Mermaid's sword. Keep it safe and finish helping the
      city before you return it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327604
    m_Localized: Not quite right. The Polish flag has white on top and red below.
      Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327605
    m_Localized: The Parliament chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327606
    m_Localized: You have the sword now. Continue to the Palace of Culture and Science.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327607
    m_Localized: Visit Parliament first, then come to the city center.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327608
    m_Localized: "Antura scattered six z\u0142oty coins around here and my wallet
      is missing!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327609
    m_Localized: "Follow the trail of coins to find it. In Poland, the z\u0142oty
      is the currency we use."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327610
    m_Localized: Yes, I found your wallet!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327611
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327612
    m_Localized: I was a Polish scientist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327613
    m_Localized: "The z\u0142oty is the currency used in Poland."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327614
    m_Localized: The Palace chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327615
    m_Localized: Cross the river and go to the National Stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327616
    m_Localized: Visit the Palace of Culture first, then come to the stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327617
    m_Localized: Antura made a big mess here and everyone is sad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327618
    m_Localized: Score five goals to cheer up the crowd, then prove you know your
      sport words.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327619
    m_Localized: Think about the ball, the field, the players, and the goal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327620
    m_Localized: Take the sport quiz!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327621
    m_Localized: Poland celebrates Independence Day on 11 November.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327622
    m_Localized: Good effort! Come back and try the sport quiz again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327623
    m_Localized: The stadium chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327624
    m_Localized: Return to the Mermaid and give her back the sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327625
    m_Localized: Please follow Antura's trail and bring my sword back when the city
      is calm again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327626
    m_Localized: You found my sword. Thank you. Keep it safe a little longer and
      finish helping the other places first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327627
    m_Localized: I am a symbol of Warsaw, and I protect the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327628
    m_Localized: Now the city is calm again, and I can take it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327629
    m_Localized: Stay with me for the final quiz and the ending.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327630
    m_Localized: You finished the trip, returned the sword, and helped the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327631
    m_Localized: Now let us see what you remember.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327632
    m_Localized: Well done. You know a lot about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327633
    m_Localized: Good try. You can explore the city again and learn more.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327634
    m_Localized: Cars also move through the city streets every day.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327635
    m_Localized: Bikes are a simple way to move from place to place.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327636
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Polish history.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327637
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Polish history.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327638
    m_Localized: Copernicus is another famous person you can learn about in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327639
    m_Localized: Copernicus is another famous person you can learn about in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327640
    m_Localized: Warsaw has symbols, history, and important buildings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83658830322327641
    m_Localized: Warsaw has symbols, history, and important buildings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044096
    m_Localized: Please follow Antura's trail and bring my sword back when the city
      is calm again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044097
    m_Localized: You found my sword! You saved us!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044098
    m_Localized: I am a symbol of Warsaw, and I protect the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044099
    m_Localized: You have {0} of 7 sword pieces. Keep exploring Warsaw to find them
      all!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044100
    m_Localized: You collected all 7 pieces of my sword! Now I can make it whole
      again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044101
    m_Localized: Which colors are on the Polish flags?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044102
    m_Localized: White and red.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044103
    m_Localized: Correct.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044104
    m_Localized: Blue and red.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044105
    m_Localized: Not really. The Polish flag is white and red.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044106
    m_Localized: Green and white.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044107
    m_Localized: Not really. The Polish flag is white and red.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044108
    m_Localized: Who was Chopin?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044109
    m_Localized: A composer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044110
    m_Localized: Correct.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044111
    m_Localized: A football player.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044112
    m_Localized: Not really. Chopin was a composer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044113
    m_Localized: A king.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550743044114
    m_Localized: Not really. Chopin was a composer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238400
    m_Localized: What is the Wisla?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238401
    m_Localized: A river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238402
    m_Localized: Correct.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238403
    m_Localized: A palace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238404
    m_Localized: Not really. The Wisla is a river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238405
    m_Localized: A stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238406
    m_Localized: Not really. The Wisla is a river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238407
    m_Localized: Well done. You know enough about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238408
    m_Localized: Good try. You can explore the city again and learn more.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238409
    m_Localized: Trams are a common way to move around Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238410
    m_Localized: Buses help people travel across the city too.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238411
    m_Localized: Cars also move through the city streets every day.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238412
    m_Localized: Trams are a common way to move around Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238413
    m_Localized: Help the Mermaid first, then come to my monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238414
    m_Localized: The melody is restored. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238415
    m_Localized: I am Fryderyk Chopin. My music is part of Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238416
    m_Localized: Help at Parliament first, then come to my monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238417
    m_Localized: The melody is restored. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238418
    m_Localized: The notes are scattered around my monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238419
    m_Localized: Can you play the melody and bring them back?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238420
    m_Localized: How do I play the melody?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238421
    m_Localized: The notes are scattered around my monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238422
    m_Localized: Can you play the melody and bring them back?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238423
    m_Localized: How do I play the melody?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238424
    m_Localized: I was a Polish composer. This is a famous place in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238425
    m_Localized: I saw Antura run past Copernicus and toward the river with the Mermaid's
      sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238426
    m_Localized: Good try! Come back and play the melody again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238427
    m_Localized: The Chopin chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238428
    m_Localized: Go north-east and help Wars and Sawa by the Wisla.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238429
    m_Localized: Chopin needs help first. Then come to the river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238430
    m_Localized: Sawa is waiting by the river bend. Speak with her, then come back
      to Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238431
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you! The chest is open.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238432
    m_Localized: Sawa is back! Talk to us both to hear the rest of our story.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238433
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you! The chest is open.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238434
    m_Localized: Sawa is back! Talk to us both to hear the rest of our story.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238435
    m_Localized: Sawa is still at the river bend. Please find her.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238436
    m_Localized: Return to Wars. We are both ready.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238437
    m_Localized: "I am Sawa. The Wis\u0142a is the longest river in Poland and this
      is our home."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238438
    m_Localized: Wars is looking for me. Please speak with him first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238439
    m_Localized: "I am Sawa. The Wis\u0142a is the longest river in Poland and this
      is our home."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238440
    m_Localized: Antura ran through here too and separated me from Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238441
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238442
    m_Localized: Our story is one of the old stories of Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238443
    m_Localized: The Wisla flows through Warsaw, and our story is part of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238444
    m_Localized: Antura passed toward King Sigismund's Column in the old town.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238445
    m_Localized: Our chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238446
    m_Localized: Go west to the old town square and speak with King Sigismund. He
      may know where the sword was left.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238447
    m_Localized: Help Wars and Sawa first, then come to my square.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238448
    m_Localized: My crown is restored. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238449
    m_Localized: I am King Sigismund. My column stands in the old town near the Royal
      Castle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238450
    m_Localized: My crown is restored. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238451
    m_Localized: I am King Sigismund. My column stands in the old town near the Royal
      Castle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238452
    m_Localized: Have you found all three crown pieces?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238453
    m_Localized: Not yet. Where should I look?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238454
    m_Localized: Have you found all three crown pieces?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238455
    m_Localized: Not yet. Where should I look?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238456
    m_Localized: Search the corners of the old town square near my column.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238457
    m_Localized: The three golden pieces are glowing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238458
    m_Localized: Yes, I have all three!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238459
    m_Localized: People remember me because the capital moved to Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550747238460
    m_Localized: I heard the Mermaid's sword was left at the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432704
    m_Localized: My chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432705
    m_Localized: Continue east to the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432706
    m_Localized: Please visit King Sigismund first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432707
    m_Localized: I am Fryderyk Chopin. My music is part of Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432708
    m_Localized: Antura scattered the notes of my melody around the monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432709
    m_Localized: Come back and play the melody on the piano to restore it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432710
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Polish Houses of Parliament. Important laws are made
      here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432711
    m_Localized: Can you play the melody and bring them back?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432712
    m_Localized: How do I play the melody?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432713
    m_Localized: Listen carefully and watch the keys light up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432714
    m_Localized: Then tap them in the same order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432715
    m_Localized: I am ready to play!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432716
    m_Localized: I was a Polish composer. This is a famous place in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432717
    m_Localized: Good try! Come back and play the melody again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432718
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432719
    m_Localized: Now go to the Palace of Culture and Science.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432720
    m_Localized: The fourth sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432721
    m_Localized: Visit Parliament first, then come to the city center.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432722
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. The chest is open. Thank you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432723
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. The chest is open. Thank you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432724
    m_Localized: "I am Maria Sk\u0142odowska-Curie. I am a Polish scientist and this
      grand building fits my story."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432725
    m_Localized: "Antura scattered six z\u0142oty coins around here and my wallet
      is missing!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432726
    m_Localized: Did you follow all six coins and find my wallet?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432727
    m_Localized: Did you follow all six coins and find my wallet?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432728
    m_Localized: Not yet. Where should I look?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432729
    m_Localized: "Follow the z\u0142oty coins from this spot. Each coin leads to
      the next."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432730
    m_Localized: The last coin is right next to my wallet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432731
    m_Localized: Yes, I found your wallet!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432732
    m_Localized: I was a Polish scientist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432733
    m_Localized: I was a Polish scientist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432734
    m_Localized: The Palace chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432735
    m_Localized: The sixth sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432736
    m_Localized: Visit the Palace of Culture first, then come to the stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432737
    m_Localized: You scored all the goals! The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432738
    m_Localized: You scored all the goals! The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432739
    m_Localized: I am Robert Lewandowski. Welcome to the National Stadium!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432740
    m_Localized: Antura made a big mess here and everyone is sad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432741
    m_Localized: Great goals! Now show me how well you know your football words.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432742
    m_Localized: Great goals! Now show me how well you know your football words.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432743
    m_Localized: I need a hint.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432744
    m_Localized: Think about the ball, the field, the players, and the goal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432745
    m_Localized: Football is one of the most popular sports played here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432746
    m_Localized: Football is one of the most popular sports played here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432747
    m_Localized: The ball is what players kick across the field.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432748
    m_Localized: The goal is where players try to score.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432749
    m_Localized: The soccer field is the place where the match is played.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432750
    m_Localized: "Mazurek D\u0105browskiego is Poland's national anthem."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432751
    m_Localized: Poland celebrates Independence Day on 11 November.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432752
    m_Localized: The stadium chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432753
    m_Localized: The seventh sword piece is yours! You have all 7 pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 83663550751432754
    m_Localized: Chopin was a famous Polish composer.
    m_Metadata:
