  - m_Id: 86094460717359125
    m_Localized: Who was Chopin?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359126
    m_Localized: A composer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359127
    m_Localized: Who was Chopin?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359128
    m_Localized: A football player.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359129
    m_Localized: A composer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359130
    m_Localized: A king.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359131
    m_Localized: A football player.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359132
    m_Localized: What is the Wisla?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359133
    m_Localized: A river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359134
    m_Localized: What is the Wisla?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359135
    m_Localized: A palace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359136
    m_Localized: A river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359137
    m_Localized: A stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359138
    m_Localized: A palace.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359139
    m_Localized: Well done. You know enough about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359140
    m_Localized: Trams are a common way to move around Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359141
    m_Localized: Buses help people travel across the city too.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359142
    m_Localized: Cars also move through the city streets every day.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359143
    m_Localized: I am Fryderyk Chopin. My music is part of Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359144
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you! The chest is open.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359145
    m_Localized: Sawa is back! Talk to us both to hear the rest of our story.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359146
    m_Localized: Listen carefully and watch the keys light up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359147
    m_Localized: Then tap them in the same order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359148
    m_Localized: I am ready to play!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359149
    m_Localized: I was a Polish composer. This is a famous place in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359150
    m_Localized: Good try! Come back and play the melody again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359151
    m_Localized: Good try! Come back and play the melody again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359152
    m_Localized: Now go to the Palace of Culture and Science.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359153
    m_Localized: Go north-east and help Wars and Sawa by the Wisla.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359154
    m_Localized: Sawa is waiting by the river bend. Speak with her, then come back
      to Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359155
    m_Localized: Sawa is waiting by the river bend. Speak with her, then come back
      to Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359156
    m_Localized: I am Wars. Antura caused chaos here too, and Sawa got separated
      from me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359157
    m_Localized: "Please find her at the bend of the Wis\u0142a and bring her back
      to me."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359158
    m_Localized: "Please find her at the bend of the Wis\u0142a and bring her back
      to me."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359159
    m_Localized: Please walk back to Wars. We will tell you the rest of our story
      together.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359160
    m_Localized: Return to Wars. We are both ready.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359161
    m_Localized: Return to Wars. We are both ready.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359162
    m_Localized: Not yet. Where should I look?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359163
    m_Localized: Search the corners of the old town square near my column.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359164
    m_Localized: Antura passed toward King Sigismund's Column in the old town.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359165
    m_Localized: Antura passed toward King Sigismund's Column in the old town.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359166
    m_Localized: Go west to the old town square and speak with King Sigismund.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359167
    m_Localized: Go west to the old town square and speak with King Sigismund. He
      may know where the sword was left.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359168
    m_Localized: Help Wars and Sawa first, then come to my square.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359169
    m_Localized: I moved the capital to Warsaw long ago. Today, Parliament leads
      Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359170
    m_Localized: Antura knocked three pieces of my crown off. Find them and bring
      them back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359171
    m_Localized: Antura knocked three pieces of my crown off. Find them and bring
      them back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359172
    m_Localized: Excellent. My crown is complete again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359173
    m_Localized: Have you found all three crown pieces?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359174
    m_Localized: Not yet. Where should I look?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359175
    m_Localized: I heard the Mermaid's sword was left at the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359176
    m_Localized: I heard the Mermaid's sword was left at the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359177
    m_Localized: Continue east to the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359178
    m_Localized: Continue east to the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359179
    m_Localized: Please visit King Sigismund first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359180
    m_Localized: I also work near the Presidential Palace, and yes, I have the Mermaid's
      sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359181
    m_Localized: But first, the flag pieces were scattered. Sort the white and red
      parts back in the right order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359182
    m_Localized: But first, the flag pieces were scattered. Sort the white and red
      parts back in the right order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359183
    m_Localized: Put them in that order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359184
    m_Localized: Let us sort the flag now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359185
    m_Localized: Let us sort the flag now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359186
    m_Localized: Not quite right. The Polish flag has white on top and red below.
      Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359187
    m_Localized: Here is the Mermaid's sword. Keep it safe and finish helping the
      city before you return it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359188
    m_Localized: Not quite right. The Polish flag has white on top and red below.
      Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359189
    m_Localized: The Parliament chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359190
    m_Localized: You have the sword now. Continue to the Palace of Culture and Science.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359191
    m_Localized: Visit Parliament first, then come to the city center.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359192
    m_Localized: "Follow the trail of coins to find it. In Poland, the z\u0142oty
      is the currency we use."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359193
    m_Localized: "Antura scattered six z\u0142oty coins around here and my wallet
      is missing!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359194
    m_Localized: "Follow the trail of coins to find it. In Poland, the z\u0142oty
      is the currency we use."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359195
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359196
    m_Localized: Yes, I found your wallet!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359197
    m_Localized: Did you follow all six coins and find my wallet?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359198
    m_Localized: I was a Polish scientist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359199
    m_Localized: "The z\u0142oty is the currency used in Poland."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359200
    m_Localized: The Palace chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359201
    m_Localized: Cross the river and go to the National Stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359202
    m_Localized: Visit the Palace of Culture first, then come to the stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359203
    m_Localized: Score five goals to cheer up the crowd, then prove you know your
      sport words.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359204
    m_Localized: Antura made a big mess here and everyone is sad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359205
    m_Localized: Score five goals to cheer up the crowd, then prove you know your
      sport words.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359206
    m_Localized: Take the sport quiz!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359207
    m_Localized: Think about the ball, the field, the players, and the goal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359208
    m_Localized: Take the sport quiz!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359209
    m_Localized: Good effort! Come back and try the sport quiz again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359210
    m_Localized: Football is one of the most popular sports played here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359211
    m_Localized: Football is one of the most popular sports played here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359212
    m_Localized: The stadium chest is open now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86094460717359213
    m_Localized: Return to the Mermaid and give her back the sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489536
    m_Localized: The fifth sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489537
    m_Localized: Help the Mermaid first, then come to the river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489538
    m_Localized: Have you found all three crown pieces?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489539
    m_Localized: The Wisla flows through Warsaw, and our story is part of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489540
    m_Localized: The second sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489541
    m_Localized: Help Wars and Sawa first, then come to my square.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489542
    m_Localized: People remember me because the capital moved to Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489543
    m_Localized: The third sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489544
    m_Localized: Please visit King Sigismund first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489545
    m_Localized: Continue to the Chopin Monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489546
    m_Localized: Visit Chopin's Monument first, then come to the city center.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489547
    m_Localized: "The z\u0142oty is the currency used in Poland."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489548
    m_Localized: Cross the river and go to the National Stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489549
    m_Localized: Visit the Palace of Culture first, then come to the stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489550
    m_Localized: Return to the Mermaid so she can reassemble her sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489551
    m_Localized: "This monument stands in \u0141azienki Park in Warsaw."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489552
    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are characters from an old legend about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489553
    m_Localized: "King Sigismund III Vasa moved the capital of Poland from Krak\xF3w
      to Warsaw in 1596."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489554
    m_Localized: He is one of the most famous composers in the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489555
    m_Localized: The Palace of Culture and Science is the tallest building in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86105078631489556
    m_Localized: "The PGE Narodowy stands on the right bank of the Wis\u0142a."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373184
    m_Localized: Where do you want to go?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373185
    m_Localized: Parliament
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373186
    m_Localized: Cathedral
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373187
    m_Localized: Market Hall
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373188
    m_Localized: Panorama
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373189
    m_Localized: Centennial Hall
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373190
    m_Localized: Stay here
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373191
    m_Localized: Hallo. Do you know where we are?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373192
    m_Localized: In Torun
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373193
    m_Localized: In Warsaw
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373194
    m_Localized: Yes! It's important to listen and read all dialogs in this game.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373195
    m_Localized: We have a problem to solve. Go to the Mermaid!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373196
    m_Localized: In Wroclaw
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373197
    m_Localized: I don't know
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373198
    m_Localized: We are at town center
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373199
    m_Localized: You collected all pieces of my sword! Now I can make it whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373200
    m_Localized: I am a symbol of Warsaw, and I protect the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373201
    m_Localized: Now let us see what you remember about this adventure
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373202
    m_Localized: Help me here at the square by sorting the ways people move around
      Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373203
    m_Localized: People travel by tram, bus, train, car, and bike.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373204
    m_Localized: Get the key and open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373205
    m_Localized: The Mermaid of Warsaw is called the Syrenka.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373206
    m_Localized: She is half woman, half fish, and carries a sword and a shield.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373207
    m_Localized: You can find her on the city sign and all over Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373208
    m_Localized: Let us sort the ways people move around Warsaw!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373209
    m_Localized: I need help. What should I sort?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373210
    m_Localized: Think about tram, bus, car, and bike.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373211
    m_Localized: Get the key and open the chest!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373212
    m_Localized: I am ready to sort!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373213
    m_Localized: "Now go to the Wars and Sawa statue by the Wis\u0142a river."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373214
    m_Localized: Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373215
    m_Localized: Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373216
    m_Localized: Good try! Come back and sort the transport words again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373217
    m_Localized: The first sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373218
    m_Localized: The first sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373219
    m_Localized: Now let us see what you remember about this adventure
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373220
    m_Localized: You have {0} of 7 sword pieces. Keep exploring Warsaw to find them
      all!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373221
    m_Localized: You collected all 7 pieces of my sword! Now I can make it whole
      again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373222
    m_Localized: I am a symbol of Warsaw, and I protect the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373223
    m_Localized: Now the city is calm again. Thank you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373224
    m_Localized: Good try. You can explore the city again and learn more.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373225
    m_Localized: Well done. You know enough about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373226
    m_Localized: Good try. You can explore the city again and learn more.
    m_Metadata:
