  - m_Id: 86114544177373227
    m_Localized: Good try. You can explore the city again and learn more.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373228
    m_Localized: Not really. The Wisla is a river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373229
    m_Localized: A stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373230
    m_Localized: Not really. The Wisla is a river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373231
    m_Localized: Well done. You know enough about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373232
    m_Localized: Trams are a common way to move around Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373233
    m_Localized: Trams are a common way to move around Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373234
    m_Localized: Buses help people travel across the city too.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373235
    m_Localized: Cars also move through the city streets every day.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373236
    m_Localized: I am Wars. Antura caused chaos here too, and Sawa got separated
      from me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373237
    m_Localized: "Please find her at the bend of the Wis\u0142a and bring her back
      to me."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373238
    m_Localized: "Please find her at the bend of the Wis\u0142a and bring her back
      to me."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373239
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you! The chest is open.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373240
    m_Localized: Sawa is back! Talk to us both to hear the rest of our story.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373241
    m_Localized: The notes are scattered around my monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373242
    m_Localized: Can you play the melody and bring them back?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373243
    m_Localized: How do I play the melody?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373244
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373245
    m_Localized: Our story is one of the old stories of Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373246
    m_Localized: We are together again. Thank you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373247
    m_Localized: Antura passed toward King Sigismund's Column in the old town.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373248
    m_Localized: The Wisla flows through Warsaw, and our story is part of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373249
    m_Localized: Go west to the old town square and speak with King Sigismund.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373250
    m_Localized: The second sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373251
    m_Localized: Help the Mermaid first, then come to the river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373252
    m_Localized: Sawa is waiting by the river bend. Speak with her, then come back
      to Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373253
    m_Localized: I moved the capital to Warsaw long ago. Today, Parliament leads
      Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373254
    m_Localized: Antura knocked three pieces of my crown off. Find them and bring
      them back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373255
    m_Localized: I moved the capital to Warsaw long ago. Today, Parliament leads
      Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373256
    m_Localized: Antura knocked three pieces of my crown off. Find them and bring
      them back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373257
    m_Localized: I am King Sigismund. My column stands in the old town near the Royal
      Castle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373258
    m_Localized: Wars is looking for me. Please speak with him first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373259
    m_Localized: "I am Sawa. The Wis\u0142a is the longest river in Poland and this
      is our home."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373260
    m_Localized: Antura ran through here too and separated me from Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373261
    m_Localized: Please walk back to Wars. We will tell you the rest of our story
      together.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373262
    m_Localized: Return to Wars. We are both ready.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373263
    m_Localized: Yes, I have all three!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373264
    m_Localized: Excellent. My crown is complete again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373265
    m_Localized: The Wisla flows through Warsaw, and our story is part of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373266
    m_Localized: People remember me because the capital moved to Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373267
    m_Localized: The second sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373268
    m_Localized: The third sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373269
    m_Localized: Help Wars and Sawa first, then come to my square.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373270
    m_Localized: My crown is restored. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373271
    m_Localized: I am King Sigismund. My column stands in the old town near the Royal
      Castle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373272
    m_Localized: You fixed the flag. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373273
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Polish Houses of Parliament. Important laws are made
      here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373274
    m_Localized: Have you found all three crown pieces?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373275
    m_Localized: Not yet. Where should I look?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373276
    m_Localized: Search the corners of the old town square near my column.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373277
    m_Localized: The three golden pieces are glowing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373278
    m_Localized: Yes, I have all three!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373279
    m_Localized: Excellent. My crown is complete again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373280
    m_Localized: The flag pieces are scattered. Put them in the correct order!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373281
    m_Localized: People remember me because the capital moved to Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373282
    m_Localized: I heard the Mermaid's sword was left at the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373283
    m_Localized: The third sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373284
    m_Localized: Continue east to the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373285
    m_Localized: We are in front of the Parliment
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373286
    m_Localized: Please visit King Sigismund first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373287
    m_Localized: You fixed the flag and have the sword. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373288
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Polish Houses of Parliament. Important laws are made
      here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373289
    m_Localized: I also work near the Presidential Palace, and yes, I have the Mermaid's
      sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373290
    m_Localized: Help at Parliament first, then come to my monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373291
    m_Localized: The flag pieces are scattered. Put them in the correct order!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373292
    m_Localized: I need a hint.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373293
    m_Localized: White is on top like snow. Red is below like a red carpet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373294
    m_Localized: Put them in that order.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373295
    m_Localized: Let us sort the flag now!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373296
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373297
    m_Localized: Not quite right. The Polish flag has white on top and red below.
      Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373298
    m_Localized: The fourth sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373299
    m_Localized: Continue to the Chopin Monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373300
    m_Localized: Visit Chopin's Monument first, then come to the city center.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373301
    m_Localized: "Antura scattered six z\u0142oty coins around here and my wallet
      is missing!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373302
    m_Localized: "Follow the trail of coins to find it. In Poland, the z\u0142oty
      is the currency we use."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373303
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. The chest is open. Thank you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373304
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. The chest is open. Thank you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373305
    m_Localized: "Follow the z\u0142oty coins from this spot. Each coin leads to
      the next."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373306
    m_Localized: The last coin is right next to my wallet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373307
    m_Localized: Yes, I found your wallet!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373308
    m_Localized: You found my wallet. Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373309
    m_Localized: Not yet. Where should I look?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373310
    m_Localized: "Follow the z\u0142oty coins from this spot. Each coin leads to
      the next."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373311
    m_Localized: I was a Polish scientist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373312
    m_Localized: "The z\u0142oty is the currency used in Poland."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373313
    m_Localized: The sixth sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373314
    m_Localized: Cross the river and go to the National Stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373315
    m_Localized: Visit the Palace of Culture first, then come to the stadium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373316
    m_Localized: I am Robert Lewandowski. Welcome to the National Stadium!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373317
    m_Localized: Antura made a big mess here and everyone is sad.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373318
    m_Localized: Score five goals to cheer up the crowd, then prove you know your
      sport words.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373319
    m_Localized: You scored all the goals! The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373320
    m_Localized: I need a hint.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373321
    m_Localized: Think about the ball, the field, the players, and the goal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373322
    m_Localized: Take the sport quiz!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373323
    m_Localized: Great goals! Now show me how well you know your football words.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373324
    m_Localized: The ball is what players kick across the field.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373325
    m_Localized: The goal is where players try to score.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373326
    m_Localized: The soccer field is the place where the match is played.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373327
    m_Localized: "Mazurek D\u0105browskiego is Poland's national anthem."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373328
    m_Localized: Poland celebrates Independence Day on 11 November.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373329
    m_Localized: Good effort! Come back and try the sport quiz again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373330
    m_Localized: The goal is where players try to score.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373331
    m_Localized: Return to the Mermaid so she can reassemble her sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373332
    m_Localized: Return to the Mermaid so she can reassemble her sword.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373333
    m_Localized: The Royal Castle stands close to the old town square.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373334
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Polish history.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373335
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Polish history.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373336
    m_Localized: The Palace of Culture and Science is a famous building in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373337
    m_Localized: Copernicus is another famous person you can learn about in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373338
    m_Localized: Copernicus is another famous person you can learn about in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373339
    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are part of an old story about the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373340
    m_Localized: Warsaw has symbols, history, and important buildings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373341
    m_Localized: Warsaw has symbols, history, and important buildings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373342
    m_Localized: The Mermaid is a symbol of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373343
    m_Localized: The Mermaid is a symbol of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373344
    m_Localized: King Sigismund moved the capital to Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373345
    m_Localized: Parliament is where laws are discussed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373346
    m_Localized: Parliament is where laws are discussed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373347
    m_Localized: "Maria Sk\u0142odowska-Curie was a scientist."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373348
    m_Localized: Independence Day is on 11 November.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373349
    m_Localized: Independence Day is on 11 November.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373350
    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are characters from an old legend about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373351
    m_Localized: "King Sigismund III Vasa moved the capital of Poland from Krak\xF3w
      to Warsaw in 1596."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373352
    m_Localized: The Polish parliament is called the Sejm and the Senate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373353
    m_Localized: It is where the President of Poland works.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373354
    m_Localized: The Palace of Culture and Science is the tallest building in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86114544177373355
    m_Localized: "The PGE Narodowy stands on the right bank of the Wis\u0142a."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752320
    m_Localized: Center
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752321
    m_Localized: Parliament
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752322
    m_Localized: Chopin
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752323
    m_Localized: We are at town center
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752324
    m_Localized: You already helped me, thank you! The chest is waiting for you here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752325
    m_Localized: I am the Mermaid of Warsaw. I am a symbol of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752326
    m_Localized: The Mermaid of Warsaw is called the Syrenka.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752327
    m_Localized: She is half woman, half fish, and carries a sword and a shield.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752328
    m_Localized: Let us sort the ways people move around Warsaw!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752329
    m_Localized: I need help. What should I sort?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752330
    m_Localized: Many people ride the tram in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752331
    m_Localized: The first sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752332
    m_Localized: The first sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752333
    m_Localized: "Now go to the Wars and Sawa statue by the Wis\u0142a river."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752334
    m_Localized: I am a symbol of Warsaw, and I protect the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752335
    m_Localized: Now the city is calm again. Thank you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752336
    m_Localized: Bikes are a simple way to move from place to place.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752337
    m_Localized: Bikes are a simple way to move from place to place.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752338
    m_Localized: I am Wars. Antura caused chaos here too, and Sawa got separated
      from me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752339
    m_Localized: "Please find her at the bend of the Wis\u0142a and bring her back
      to me."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752340
    m_Localized: The notes are scattered around my monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752341
    m_Localized: Can you play the melody and bring them back?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752342
    m_Localized: I was a Polish composer. This is a famous place in Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752343
    m_Localized: The Wisla flows through Warsaw, and our story is part of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752344
    m_Localized: The fifth sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752345
    m_Localized: The second sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752346
    m_Localized: Help the Mermaid first, then come to the river.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752347
    m_Localized: Sawa is waiting by the river bend. Speak with her, then come back
      to Wars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752348
    m_Localized: My crown is restored. The chest is yours.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752349
    m_Localized: I am King Sigismund. My column stands in the old town near the Royal
      Castle.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752350
    m_Localized: Wars is looking for me. Please speak with him first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752351
    m_Localized: "I am Sawa. The Wis\u0142a is the longest river in Poland and this
      is our home."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752352
    m_Localized: Search the corners of the old town square near my column.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752353
    m_Localized: The three golden pieces are glowing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752354
    m_Localized: I heard the Mermaid's sword was left at the Houses of Parliament.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752355
    m_Localized: Antura passed toward King Sigismund's Column in the old town.
