  - m_Id: 86116720429752371
    m_Localized: The Constitution of 3 May is an important day in Poland.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752372
    m_Localized: Not quite right. The Polish flag has white on top and red below.
      Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752373
    m_Localized: The fourth sword piece is yours!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86116720429752374
    m_Localized: Continue to the Chopin Monument.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
