    m_Localized: Wars and Sawa are characters from an old legend about Warsaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86199584680828936
    m_Localized: Their names are said to be hidden inside the name "Warszawa."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 86199584680828937
    m_Localized: "King Sigismund III Vasa moved the capital of Poland from Krak\xF3w
      to Warsaw in 1596."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
